                        "heroImageUrl": "",
                        "heroAlt": "",
                        "bodyHtml": "<h3><strong>Wilderness First Aid Certification Course </strong></h3><h3><strong>At a glance </strong></h3><h3><br></h3><p><strong>TUITION - </strong>$206 for members, $256 for non-members</p><p class=\"enroll-closed\"><strong>Applications are currently closed.</strong> This program isn\u2019t accepting new applications right now \u2014 watch the <a href=\"/events\">events calendar</a> for the next session.</p><p><strong>CLASS SIZE LIMIT - 30 (AdvancedRegistration Required)</strong></p><p><strong>COURSE DURATION - 2 days / 16 hours</strong></p><p>This course will be taught both indoors and outdoors. </p><p>Questions? <a href=\"mailto:clubcomms@spokanemountaineers.org\"> </a><a href=\"mailto:clubcomms@spokanemountaineers.org\">Wilderness Medicine</a></p><p>Not yet a member?</p><p><a href=\"https://donorbox.org/spokane-mountaineers-membership-2\"><strong>Join Today!</strong></a></p><p><img data-asset=\"schools/wildernessFirstAidCourse_1.jpg\" alt=\"wildernessFirstAidCourse diagram\"></p><h1>Wilderness First Aid</h1><h1>A Certification Course taught by Longleaf Wilderness Medicine</h1><p>Wilderness First Aid Knowledge is one of the most important skill sets to have in the backcountry. </p><p>Wilderness First Aid teaches skills necessary when professional medical help is an indefinite time or distance away.</p><p>Environmental aspects of backcountry emergency situations will be covered in detail.</p><p>We partner with <a href=\"https://www.longleafmedical.com/\">Longleaf Wilderness Medicine</a> to teach this course over two eight-hour days. </p><p>The certification received upon completion of the course is good for two years.</p><p><strong>Dates -</strong> October 25-26, 2025</p><p><strong>Location - Turnbull National Wildlife Refuge</strong></p><p><strong>Cost -</strong> $206 for members, $256 for nonmembers (includes $6 fee for online registration on Long Leaf Website). </p><p><strong>Member Discount Code - M</strong>embers can get $50 off. Find code on June 4, 2025 Post or on the Event on the <span class=\"muted\">Club Calendar on October 25</span> on the member website <span class=\"muted\"><strong>Click Here</strong></span> (requires member log in)</p><p><span class=\"muted\"><strong>Registration -</strong> Long Leaf Website</span> </p><p>Questions? <a href=\"mailto:clubcomms@spokanemountaineers.org\">Wilderness Medicine</a></p>",
